import { Box, Grid, Icon, ImageList, ImageListItem, Paper, Stack, Typography } from "@material-ui/core";
import Masonry, { ResponsiveMasonry } from "react-responsive-masonry";
import avatar from "../images/profilePic.jpg";


function AboutMe() {
    return (

        
        <ResponsiveMasonry
        columnsCountBreakPoints={{350: 1, 750: 2, 900: 2}}
    >
        <Masonry style={{margin:'auto', width:'52rem'}} gutter='1rem'>
           <Paper elevation={2} sx={{p:'0.3rem', borderRadius:'0.5rem', width:'28rem'}}>
               <Grid container>
                   <Grid item flexGrow='1'>
                       <Box sx={{width:'100%', height:'100%',display:'flex', alignItems:'center', justifyContent:'center', backgroundColor:'re'}}>
                           <Box component='img' width='9rem' src={avatar} sx={{borderRadius:'0.5rem', border:'1px solid #d3d3d3', p:10/12}}/>
                       </Box>
                   </Grid>
                   <Grid item flexGrow='0.6'>
                   <Box sx={{width:'100%', height:'12rem', display:'flex', flexDirection:'column', justifyContent:'center', alignItems:'center', backgroundColor:'blu', gap:1.5}}>
                           <Typography sx={{fontSize:'1.5rem', fontFamily:'sans-serif', fontWeight:'600', color:'success.dark'}}>
                               Brian Ojoh Mile
                           </Typography>
                           <Typography sx={{fontWeight:'600'}}>Full Stack Developer</Typography>
                           <Typography sx={{fontWeight:'600'}}>Laurel, MD</Typography>
                           <Stack direction='row' spacing={1} sx={{border:2, p:1, borderRadius:'1rem', color:'error.main'}}>
                               <Icon baseClassName='fab' className='fa-github' sx={{fontSize:'1.8rem'}} />
                               <Icon baseClassName='fab' className='fa-linkedin' sx={{fontSize:'1.8rem'}} />
                           </Stack>
                       </Box>
                   </Grid>
               </Grid>
           </Paper>
        </Masonry>
    </ResponsiveMasonry>
    
    )
}

export default AboutMe;
